License System Features:

| Feature              | Implementation                                   |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
| **Key Format**       | `MGKY-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-SIGN` (Ed25519 signed) |
| **Hardware Binding** | Fingerprint hash stored at activation            |
| **Tier System**      | Trial → Standard → Pro → Enterprise → Lifetime   |
| **Offline Grace**    | 24-hour offline usage after last validation      |
| **Usage Tracking**   | Daily page limits with warning thresholds        |
| **Auto-Reset**       | Daily quota resets at midnight local time        |


Integration:
Uses hardware-fingerprint.js for machine binding
Uses custom-encryption.js for secure storage
Communicates with license server for activation/validation